{"tid":316041,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街啦共產黨又屌王者榮耀","createTime":"2017-07-10T12:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T01:33:13.000Z","uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1835abfd5cfc2fe1a52906b6a53a7db5b8c8ddd","tid":316041,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"【「王者榮耀」再被內地官媒批評】<br />\n【新華社：消費歷史形成文化誤讀】<br />\n<br />\n內地官方媒體再次批評騰訊，指手機遊戲「王者榮耀」扭曲歷史人物。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》以「手遊不應遊戲歷史」為題，批評「王者榮耀」一邊消費歷史文化，一邊歪曲歷史人物，形成文化誤讀以及價值錯亂。<br />\n<br />\n「王者榮耀」在遊戲中，將意圖刺殺秦始皇「荊軻」，改為美女刺客，又將三國時代劉備，描寫成黑幫教父。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#王者榮耀　#新華社　#騰訊　#手遊　#遊戲歷史<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日又跌到仆街"},{"pid":"1368423217c95f7d5f6ea14048678253b0ad3ec3","tid":316041,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"愈屌愈無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下劑會唔會出文屌點解唔叫榮耀王者要叫王者榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cae74ef2d95e5031d1fa2fd5cad55b510d6cff5","tid":316041,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4486f44a631582ea3e383e43db988464a08720a5","tid":316041,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶是我<br />\n我就是蝴蝶"},{"pid":"5e375c79f57e81bb6093944172ef0cf03e7df4f4","tid":316041,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"係時候入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc52a5de42d266d06e61ef653229f61505f5e21","tid":316041,"uid":16101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18eb2f1cb6c277e83d6d27b882a258ae46b608e6","tid":316041,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T00:04:24.000Z","msg":"上綱上線 擺明傾唔掂數"},{"pid":"38726e2cc85926e4764ca0e35754f19458dd1